Package: bcrypt
Type: Package
Title: OpenBSD Blowfish Password Hashing Algorithm
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Jeroen", "Ooms", , "jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: An implementation the OpenBSD blowfish password hashing algorithm,
    as described in "A Future-Adaptable Password Scheme" by Niels Provos. The
    implementation is derived from the 'py-bcrypt' module for Python which is a
    wrapper for the OpenBSD implementation.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Imports: openssl
